1. *Uđeš* u svoju sobu i skloniš se od svijeta. (You enter your room and hide away from the world.)

2. On se ugleda da *uđeš* u sobu. (He gestured for you to enter the room.)

3. On uđe u sobu i počne da pjeva. (He entered the room and started to sing.)

4. *Uđeš* li u sobu sama? (Do you enter the room alone?)

5. Ona *uđe* u sobu i zatvorila vrata. (She entered the room and closed the door.)